        <h2>Coorg</h2>

        <p>A hill station known for its coffee plantations and picturesque scenery.</p>

        <p>Coorg offers scenic views, coffee estates, and a calm environment for a relaxing getaway.</p>

        <img src="https://static2.tripoto.com/media/filter/tst/img/1889288/TripDocument/1605545614_1605545609694.jpg" alt="Coorg">
       
        <p>Coorg, or Kodagu, is a scenic hill station in Karnataka, known for its lush coffee plantations, pleasant climate, and stunning landscapes. Attractions include Abbey Falls, Nisargadhama, and the Dubare Elephant Camp. Coorg is rich in Kodava culture and traditions, with festivals like Carthigai and Puttari. It also offers abundant wildlife through parks like Nagarhole National Park. Famous for its spicy cuisine and activities like trekking and rafting, Coorg provides a perfect blend of adventure and relaxation.</p>

